lead_paragraph: Exclusive talks between Silvio Berlusconi's Fininvest and a group of Chinese investors over the sale of a stake in soccer club AC Milan will last one month, a source close to the matter said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Berlusconi's AC Milan Talks With Chinese to Last One Month: Source
